254
00:21:59,970 --> 00:22:01,513
Có ai không!

255
00:23:00,363 --> 00:23:01,948
Bố?

256
00:23:03,825 --> 00:23:05,077
Samuel.

257
00:23:06,953 --> 00:23:08,747
Con đã làm gì?

258
00:23:33,688 --> 00:23:36,483
DANIELLE MOONSTAR
